<section>
  <div
    class="mx-auto w-full lg:px-24 max-w-7xl md:px-12 items-center px-8 py-24 scroll-mt-12"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <div>
          <img src="/FAQ.svg" alt="frequently asked question">
          <p class="text-base mt-4 text-zinc-500 text-center">
            ANSWERS TO COMMONLY ASKED QUESTIONS
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        x-data="{
  activeAccordion: '',
  setActiveAccordion(id) {
  this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id
  }
  }"
        class="relative w-full mx-auto self-center font-normal lg:col-span-2"
      >
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
          <span class="w-full">What are the hours of operation for 5 Stars Cleaning LLC ?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500 -rotate-[45deg]"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path>
           </svg>
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              The hours of operation for 5 Star Cleaning are Monday to Friday, from 8am to 6pm. 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span class="w-full"
              >What areas do 5 Star Cleaning serve ?</span
            >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              5 Star Cleaning LLC services all areas within the Twin Cities Metropolitan Area. This includes a wide range of locations within and around the cities of Minneapolis and St. Paul. Please contact us directly for more specific information about our service areas.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span class="w-full"
              >What is the difference between a ‘Deep Cleaning’ and ‘Basic Cleaning’ services ?</span
            >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              <div class="flex">
              <img src="/Basic.svg" class="w-24"  alt="window cleaning">
              <p><span class="font-bold">Basic Cleaning</span>: This service helps with maintaining cleanliness and keeps your living space neat and tidy. This service is typically done on a weekly and bi-weekly basis and targets surface-level areas.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex">
              <img src="/Deep.svg" class="w-24" alt="vacuum cleaning">
              <p><span class="font-bold">Deep Cleaning</span>: A more detail cleaning service that helps target hard-to-reach areas and tackles deep seeded dirt and grime that can accumulate over time. This service goes beyond the surface level to ensure cleanliness and is typically done bi-annually or quarterly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span class="w-full"
              >How much does an cleaning estimate cost at 5 Stars Cleaning LLC ?</span
            >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Nothing! There are no costs for an quote on an estimate for any of our services. Schedule your free estimate by contacting us via email ( five5.starss.cleaning@gmail.com) or give us call at  +1 (651) 506 9418.  
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span class="w-full"
              >How long does 5 Star Cleaning LLC take to respond to a cleaning service inquiry ? </span
            >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            x-collapse=""
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              5-Star Cleaning LLC is committed to providing excellent service. You can expect a response within 1-2 business days for any cleaning service inquiries. 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          </div>
        </div>
</section>
